About Page (5-6 Points)

Headline: A catchy tagline or mission statement.
Example: "Where Style Meets Comfort – Your Go-To Saloon for Premium Grooming."
Brief History: A short paragraph about your saloon's origin and journey.
Example: "Founded in 2010, [Saloon Name] has been a trusted name in grooming, offering top-notch services to our community."
Team Introduction: Highlight your team with photos and short bios.
Example: "Meet our talented stylists and barbers who bring passion and expertise to every cut."
Core Values: Share what makes your saloon unique.
Example: "We believe in quality, inclusivity, and making every client feel special."
Call to Action (CTA): Encourage visitors to book an appointment or explore services.
Example: "Ready for a fresh look? Book your appointment today!"





Contact Page (5-6 Points)

Contact Form: A simple form for name, email, phone, and message.
Example: "Have a question? Drop us a message, and we’ll get back to you soon!"
Location Details: Address with an embedded Google Map.
Example: "Visit us at [Address] or use the map below to find us."
Phone and Email: Display your contact information prominently.
Example: "Call us at [Phone Number] or email us at [Email Address]."
Business Hours: List your operating hours.
Example: "We’re open Monday to Saturday, 9 AM to 7 PM."
Social Media Links: Icons linking to your social media profiles.
Example: "Follow us on Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter for updates and promotions."




Services Page (5-6 Points)

Service Categories: Group services into sections (e.g., Haircuts, Styling, Shaves).
Example: "Explore our range of services designed to meet your grooming needs."
Service List: A list of services with brief descriptions.
Example: "Classic Haircut – $30 | Precision cuts tailored to your style."
Pricing: Display prices for each service (optional).
Example: "Beard Trim – $15 | Keep your beard looking sharp and well-groomed.
Booking CTA: Add a "Book Now" button for each service.
Example: "Ready to book? Click here to schedule your appointment."
Testimonials: Include a few client reviews about your services.
Example: "‘Best haircut I’ve ever had!’ – [Client Name]."
Service Images: Add high-quality images of your services.
Example: "Check out our gallery to see the results of our work." 